WEBVTT

00:00:35.900 --> 00:00:37.500
Departure.

00:00:42.866 --> 00:00:43.666
The man

00:00:44.200 --> 00:00:45.700
You explain to me.

00:00:45.766 --> 00:00:47.633
Why didn't you go to work yesterday?

00:00:47.866 --> 00:00:50.200
Wasn't yesterday Sunday?

00:00:50.466 --> 00:00:52.900
Why?

00:00:53.266 --> 00:00:55.333
Depends on the company paying you.

00:00:55.333 --> 00:00:57.066
Take money from teachers.

00:00:57.133 --> 00:01:00.233
You must listen to the teacher.

00:01:03.466 --> 00:01:04.833
That is salary.

00:01:05.133 --> 00:01:08.233
It is Lao Tzu's hard-earned money.